PN,30801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775527075
OL,3,CBoy who had collapsed lungs as child
OL,4,Cwins karate medal at world
OL,5,Cchampionships
OL,7,FA schoolboy who spent time on life
OL,8,Fsupport as a baby and suffered
OL,9,Fcollapsed lungs during childhood has
OL,10,Fbeen praised for his "extraordinary"
OL,11,Fjourney after winning a medal at the
OL,12,FWorld Karate Championships.
OL,14,FBen Cotter, 15, from Glasgow, said it
OL,15,Ffeels "amazing" to compete and travel
OL,16,Fround the world, particularly after
OL,17,Fhis difficult start in life which saw
OL,18,Fhim taken to neonatal intensive care
OL,19,Fas soon as he was born.
OL,26,@rD@VOUrD@dO]wD@GOUwD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775527075
OL,3,CBoy who had collapsed lungs as child
OL,4,Cwins karate medal at world
OL,5,Cchampionships
OL,7,FHe was readmitted to hospital in
OL,8,Fcritical condition at four weeks old
OL,9,Fand placed on life support and was
OL,10,Flater diagnosed with bronchomalacia `
OL,11,Fa condition which means the airways
OL,12,Fare abnormally soft and prone to
OL,13,Fcollapse, meaning his breathing could
OL,14,Fstop.
OL,16,FDuring early childhood his breathing
OL,17,Fsometimes stopped without warning and
OL,18,Fhe had to be resuscitated on several
OL,19,Foccasions by medical teams, and
OL,20,Fsometimes by his parents.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775527075
OL,3,CBoy who had collapsed lungs as child
OL,4,Cwins karate medal at world
OL,5,Cchampionships
OL,7,FHe suffered a collapsed lung several
OL,8,Ftimes which left him with permanent
OL,9,Flung damage and was often placed on
OL,10,Foxygen.
OL,12,FHowever he did not let his health
OL,13,Fproblems stand in the way of his
OL,14,Finterest in sport and took up karate
OL,15,Fat the age of four.
OL,17,FThe teenager is now a karate black
OL,18,Fbelt and won a bronze medal while
OL,19,Frepresenting Scotland in his age group
OL,20,Fat the JSKA World Karate Championships
OL,21,Fin Matsuyama, Japan, in November.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775527075
OL,3,CBoy who had collapsed lungs as child
OL,4,Cwins karate medal at world
OL,5,Cchampionships
OL,7,FAt the event he was also graded Shodan
OL,8,F` first degree black belt ` in front
OL,9,Fof SKA world chief instructor Nagaki
OL,10,FMitsuru Shihan.
OL,12,FBen said: "There was a point where
OL,13,Fdoctors were worried about whether I
OL,14,Fwould survive and whether it would
OL,15,Faffect things like learning and
OL,16,Fwalking. I felt like I was always
OL,17,Fwearing a hospital wrist band.
OL,26,@tD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775527075
OL,3,CBoy who had collapsed lungs as child
OL,4,Cwins karate medal at world
OL,5,Cchampionships
OL,7,F"Even when I started karate I remember
OL,8,Fbeing really tired because my left
OL,9,Flung had to do most of the work, but
OL,10,Fit's just something that's always been
OL,11,Fpart of my life.
OL,13,F"Competing now and travelling around
OL,14,Fthe world for karate ` a sport that's
OL,15,Fgiven me so much ` is amazing,
OL,16,Fespecially when I think about where I
OL,17,Fstarted.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775527075
OL,3,CBoy who had collapsed lungs as child
OL,4,Cwins karate medal at world
OL,5,Cchampionships
OL,7,F"Competing in Japan was incredible,
OL,8,Fthe Ehime Prefectural Budokan is
OL,9,Fcompletely different to what we're
OL,10,Fused to here.
OL,12,F"In the UK, I compete in leisure
OL,13,Fcentres but there you feel like a
OL,14,Fgladiator competing in these
OL,15,Fincredible structures of wood and
OL,16,Fmetal with statues everywhere. There's
OL,17,Fa real sense of history there. Walking
OL,18,Fin to compete was an amazing
OL,19,Fexperience."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775527075
OL,3,CBoy who had collapsed lungs as child
OL,4,Cwins karate medal at world
OL,5,Cchampionships
OL,7,FBen's father Nicholas, 39, is a fourth
OL,8,Fdan black belt and trains his son
OL,9,Ftwice a week.
OL,11,FThe teenager, a pupil at Kelvinside
OL,12,FAcademy in Glasgow, is also a keen
OL,13,Frugby player, and plays inside centre
OL,14,Ffor West of Scotland and his school.
OL,16,FThe 15-year-old, who wants to go on to
OL,17,Fstudy medicine, also earned the title
OL,18,Fof British Kumite champion in karate
OL,19,Fin London in January and is looking
OL,20,Fforward to taking part in future
OL,21,Fkarate events.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775527075
OL,3,CBoy who had collapsed lungs as child
OL,4,Cwins karate medal at world
OL,5,Cchampionships
OL,7,FHe said: "Karate has given me so many
OL,8,Fexperiences and taken me around the
OL,9,Fworld, so it's something I'll keep
OL,10,Fdoing for the rest of my life.
OL,12,F"The next big championships are in
OL,13,FItaly next year, and I'm already
OL,14,Ffocused on getting better and pushing
OL,15,Ffurther. Winning in London was another
OL,16,Fproud moment."
OL,26,@oD@JOUtD@AOUxD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775527075
OL,3,CBoy who had collapsed lungs as child
OL,4,Cwins karate medal at world
OL,5,Cchampionships
OL,7,FKelvinside Academy rector Daniel Wyatt
OL,8,Fsaid: "Ben's journey has been nothing
OL,9,Fshort of extraordinary. From a life-
OL,10,Fthreatening collapsed lung to a
OL,11,Fdetermined young athlete, he has
OL,12,Fdefied the odds at every turn.
OL,14,F"At just 15, winning a bronze medal at
OL,15,Fthe Karate World Championships in
OL,16,FJapan is a testament not only to his
OL,17,Fskill but to his resilience,
OL,18,Fdiscipline and unwavering spirit."
OL,26,@pD@GOUvD@AOUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775527075
OL,3,CBoy who had collapsed lungs as child
OL,4,Cwins karate medal at world
OL,5,Cchampionships
OL,7,FMike McCusker, Ben's coach at Hokushin
OL,8,FKarate Academy, said: "Watching him
OL,9,Fgrow from that determined young boy
OL,10,Finto the martial artist he is today
OL,11,Fhas been an honour.
OL,13,F"He first came to train with me as a
OL,14,Fsmall boy who was often frail and
OL,15,Funwell, but despite those early
OL,16,Fchallenges, he never asked for special
OL,17,Ftreatment and was expected to train
OL,18,Fand push himself just like every other
OL,19,Fstudent.
OL,26,@pD@WOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775527075
OL,3,CBoy who had collapsed lungs as child
OL,4,Cwins karate medal at world
OL,5,Cchampionships
OL,7,F"Earning a black belt is a milestone
OL,8,Ffew reach, but to do so in Japan ` the
OL,9,Fbirthplace of Shotokan karate ` makes
OL,10,Fthe achievement even more remarkable.
OL,12,F"Ben's success is a testament to his
OL,13,Fperseverance, courage and spirit."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUuD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
